						               													<description>When Bad Karma Strikes, Pass It On To Other Players!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can travel down life through good deeds or bad deeds, but karma will follow you either way. In Pass The Karma, your best tactic is to collect that bad karma now and pass it on to your opponents to get the win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This 2nd entry into the Karma Crystals game collection adds a set of elemental shards and a new way to pass on your bad karma to other players. This game also introduces a Karma Crystal scoring system to track all that bad Karma going around. Last but not least, you get 12 new monster elemental cards for your collector&amp;rsquo;s deck!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Collect up to elemental elemental shards (up to TWO per type) to represent your forward movement through your karma travels. If you get too many per type, you get Karma Crystals and get a chance to pass their reverse-move effect on your score to other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Roll dice to work with the various monster elemental cards - monsters are the good guys and help you win! Determine how many karma moves you score per roll and collect your elemental shards for the match, or pass on your no-match karma to another player! When you get elemental shards of FOUR types, that triggers the end of the game and scores are tallied at the end of the round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In addition to the unique dice matching game mechanic, a unique auto player system is used to facilitate up to EIGHT total players per game. The game also provides an easy way to track multiple game wins for playoffs in case you have more than 15 to 20 minutes to play. No paper score cards and pencil needed - just Karma Crystals, crystal cubes and elemental shards to track and build your score.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
